item.title: CVE-2022-1609|2024-08-03T00:10:03.591Z -- unknown -- school-management-pro
item.description: The School Management WordPress plugin before 9.9.7 contains an obfuscated backdoor injected in it's license checking code that registers a REST API handler, allowing an unauthenticated attacker to execute arbitrary PHP code on the site.
